{"tid":2005777,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"入黎估法官","createTime":"2020-05-07T10:34:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T10:41:29.000Z","uid":106672,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e1b4b4bffaf238da9bc3e3444ce5fc4183627ea2","tid":2005777,"uid":106672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T10:34:07.000Z","msg":"去年 9 月 15 日，北角及炮台山一帶發生多宗白衣人與示威者打鬥事件。當中一名持摺凳追打示威者的中年白衣人今日在東區裁判法院，承認一項管有攻擊性武器並有所意圖罪。辯方向法庭呈上由福建組織撰寫的求情信，並指被告是因為其弟弟遭「私了」才一時衝動「幫拖」；惟裁判官不接受此說法，指片段可見被告一直手持摺凳在街上行走，反問辯方「Impulsive?（一時衝動？）」。案件押後至 5 月 21 日判刑，以待索取背景及社會服務令報告，被告須還押候判。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"705a1a529dfad81ceb92cf1423e4f3d0c62febf7","tid":2005777,"uid":19527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T10:35:02.000Z","msg":"錢禮？"},{"pid":"d4e83710e12c443969a464c8210c63c5931d5e30","tid":2005777,"uid":84408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T10:37:28.000Z","msg":"正常官 話知佢乜名<br />\n無人想知"},{"pid":"1247fc8752f6ad3a3e8267aa451fa2f9c6c04046","tid":2005777,"uid":106672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"705a1a529dfad81ceb92cf1423e4f3d0c62febf7","tid":2005777,"uid":19527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T10:35:02.000Z","msg":"錢禮？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T10:37:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />心水清，條友都算抵死，中錢禮"},{"pid":"89a1ce6937b34075c408ff3111aff5f4c1f3be98","tid":2005777,"uid":335434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1247fc8752f6ad3a3e8267aa451fa2f9c6c04046","tid":2005777,"uid":106672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"705a1a529dfad81ceb92cf1423e4f3d0c62febf7","tid":2005777,"uid":19527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T10:35:02.000Z","msg":"錢禮？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T10:37:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/no